{
  "video_id": "pk35J2u8KqY",
  "title": "The human insights missing from big data | Tricia Wang",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12705.0,
      "end_time": 14250.0,
      "text": "In ancient Greece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15256.0,
      "end_time": 19199.0,
      "text": "when anyone from slaves to soldiers, poets and politicians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19223.0,
      "end_time": 23226.0,
      "text": "needed to make a big decision on life&#39;s most important questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23251.0,
      "end_time": 24642.0,
      "text": "like, \"Should I get married?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24666.0,
      "end_time": 26523.0,
      "text": "or \"Should we embark on this voyage?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26547.0,
      "end_time": 29475.0,
      "text": "or \"Should our army advance into this territory?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29499.0,
      "end_time": 32770.0,
      "text": "they all consulted the oracle."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32840.0,
      "end_time": 34280.0,
      "text": "So this is how it worked:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34304.0,
      "end_time": 37416.0,
      "text": "you would bring her a question and you would get on your knees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37440.0,
      "end_time": 39311.0,
      "text": "and then she would go into this trance."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39335.0,
      "end_time": 40884.0,
      "text": "It would take a couple of days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40908.0,
      "end_time": 43710.0,
      "text": "and then eventually she would come out of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43950.0,
      "end_time": 45631.0,
      "text": "giving you her predictions as your answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46730.0,
      "end_time": 49296.0,
      "text": "From the oracle bones of ancient China"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49320.0,
      "end_time": 51665.0,
      "text": "to ancient Greece to Mayan calendars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51689.0,
      "end_time": 53985.0,
      "text": "people have craved for prophecy"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54900.0,
      "end_time": 57146.0,
      "text": "in order to find out what&#39;s going to happen next."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58336.0,
      "end_time": 61574.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because we all want to make the right decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61599.0,
      "end_time": 63144.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want to miss something."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63712.0,
      "end_time": 65455.0,
      "text": "The future is scary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65479.0,
      "end_time": 68196.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s much nicer knowing that we can make a decision"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68220.0,
      "end_time": 70202.0,
      "text": "with some assurance of the outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70899.0,
      "end_time": 72510.0,
      "text": "Well, we have a new oracle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72534.0,
      "end_time": 74679.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s name is big data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74703.0,
      "end_time": 78642.0,
      "text": "or we call it \"Watson\" or \"deep learning\" or \"neural net.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79160.0,
      "end_time": 83172.0,
      "text": "And these are the kinds of questions we ask of our oracle now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83196.0,
      "end_time": 87118.0,
      "text": "like, \"What&#39;s the most efficient way to ship these phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87142.0,
      "end_time": 88964.0,
      "text": "from China to Sweden?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 88989.0,
      "end_time": 90789.0,
      "text": "Or, \"What are the odds"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90813.0,
      "end_time": 94176.0,
      "text": "of my child being born with a genetic disorder?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94772.0,
      "end_time": 98160.0,
      "text": "Or, \"What are the sales volume we can predict for this product?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99928.0,
      "end_time": 103975.0,
      "text": "I have a dog. Her name is Elle, and she hates the rain."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103999.0,
      "end_time": 107304.0,
      "text": "And I have tried everything to untrain her."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107329.0,
      "end_time": 110100.0,
      "text": "But because I have failed at this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110124.0,
      "end_time": 113410.0,
      "text": "I also have to consult an oracle, called Dark Sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113434.0,
      "end_time": 115690.0,
      "text": "every time before we go on a walk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115930.0,
      "end_time": 118670.0,
      "text": "for very accurate weather predictions in the next 10 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121355.0,
      "end_time": 122658.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s so sweet."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123647.0,
      "end_time": 129354.0,
      "text": "So because of all of this, our oracle is a $122 billion industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 129826.0,
      "end_time": 133202.0,
      "text": "Now, despite the size of this industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 133226.0,
      "end_time": 135682.0,
      "text": "the returns are surprisingly low."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136162.0,
      "end_time": 138656.0,
      "text": "Investing in big data is easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138680.0,
      "end_time": 140613.0,
      "text": "but using it is hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141801.0,
      "end_time": 145840.0,
      "text": "Over 73 percent of big data projects aren&#39;t even profitable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 145865.0,
      "end_time": 148296.0,
      "text": "and I have executives coming up to me saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148320.0,
      "end_time": 150108.0,
      "text": "\"We&#39;re experiencing the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150133.0,
      "end_time": 151886.0,
      "text": "We invested in some big data system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151910.0,
      "end_time": 154878.0,
      "text": "and our employees aren&#39;t making better decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154902.0,
      "end_time": 158640.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re certainly not coming up with more breakthrough ideas.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158734.0,
      "end_time": 161918.0,
      "text": "So this is all really interesting to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 161942.0,
      "end_time": 163952.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m a technology ethnographer."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 164450.0,
      "end_time": 167130.0,
      "text": "I study and I advise companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167380.0,
      "end_time": 169521.0,
      "text": "on the patterns of how people use technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 169545.0,
      "end_time": 172222.0,
      "text": "and one of my interest areas is data."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172247.0,
      "end_time": 177440.0,
      "text": "So why is having more data not helping us make better decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 177464.0,
      "end_time": 180247.0,
      "text": "especially for companies who have all these resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 180271.0,
      "end_time": 182600.0,
      "text": "to invest in these big data systems?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182310.0,
      "end_time": 184429.0,
      "text": "Why isn&#39;t it getting any easier for them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 185810.0,
      "end_time": 188444.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;ve witnessed the struggle firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 189194.0,
      "end_time": 192678.0,
      "text": "In 2009, I started a research position with Nokia."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 193520.0,
      "end_time": 194209.0,
      "text": "And at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 194234.0,
      "end_time": 197392.0,
      "text": "Nokia was one of the largest cell phone companies in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 197416.0,
      "end_time": 200618.0,
      "text": "dominating emerging markets like China, Mexico and India --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 200642.0,
      "end_time": 203144.0,
      "text": "all places where I had done a lot of research"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 203168.0,
      "end_time": 205844.0,
      "text": "on how low-income people use technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 205868.0,
      "end_time": 208198.0,
      "text": "And I spent a lot of extra time in China"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 208222.0,
      "end_time": 210814.0,
      "text": "getting to know the informal economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 210838.0,
      "end_time": 213239.0,
      "text": "So I did things like working as a street vendor"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 213263.0,
      "end_time": 215837.0,
      "text": "selling dumplings to construction workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215861.0,
      "end_time": 217219.0,
      "text": "Or I did fieldwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 217243.0,
      "end_time": 220201.0,
      "text": "spending nights and days in internet caf√©s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220225.0,
      "end_time": 222771.0,
      "text": "hanging out with Chinese youth, so I could understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222795.0,
      "end_time": 225780.0,
      "text": "how they were using games and mobile phones"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 225103.0,
      "end_time": 228473.0,
      "text": "and using it between moving from the rural areas to the cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 230155.0,
      "end_time": 234820.0,
      "text": "Through all of this qualitative evidence that I was gathering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 234106.0,
      "end_time": 236930.0,
      "text": "I was starting to see so clearly"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236954.0,
      "end_time": 241426.0,
      "text": "that a big change was about to happen among low-income Chinese people."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242840.0,
      "end_time": 247207.0,
      "text": "Even though they were surrounded by advertisements for luxury products"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 247231.0,
      "end_time": 250726.0,
      "text": "like fancy toilets -- who wouldn&#39;t want one? --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250750.0,
      "end_time": 253640.0,
      "text": "and apartments and cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 253664.0,
      "end_time": 255483.0,
      "text": "through my conversations with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 255508.0,
      "end_time": 259349.0,
      "text": "I found out that the ads the actually enticed them the most"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 259373.0,
      "end_time": 261368.0,
      "text": "were the ones for iPhones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261392.0,
      "end_time": 264445.0,
      "text": "promising them this entry into this high-tech life."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 265289.0,
      "end_time": 268452.0,
      "text": "And even when I was living with them in urban slums like this one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 268476.0,
      "end_time": 271472.0,
      "text": "I saw people investing over half of their monthly income"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 271496.0,
      "end_time": 273119.0,
      "text": "into buying a phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 273143.0,
      "end_time": 275445.0,
      "text": "and increasingly, they were \"shanzhai,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 275469.0,
      "end_time": 278857.0,
      "text": "which are affordable knock-offs of iPhones and other brands."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 280123.0,
      "end_time": 281748.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re very usable."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 282710.0,
      "end_time": 284320.0,
      "text": "Does the job."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 284570.0,
      "end_time": 290359.0,
      "text": "And after years of living with migrants and working with them"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 290383.0,
      "end_time": 293817.0,
      "text": "and just really doing everything that they were doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293841.0,
      "end_time": 297438.0,
      "text": "I started piecing all these data points together --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 297462.0,
      "end_time": 300585.0,
      "text": "from the things that seem random, like me selling dumplings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 300609.0,
      "end_time": 302412.0,
      "text": "to the things that were more obvious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 302437.0,
      "end_time": 305669.0,
      "text": "like tracking how much they were spending on their cell phone bills."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 305693.0,
      "end_time": 308332.0,
      "text": "And I was able to create this much more holistic picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 308356.0,
      "end_time": 309512.0,
      "text": "of what was happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 309536.0,
      "end_time": 311258.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s when I started to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 311282.0,
      "end_time": 314791.0,
      "text": "that even the poorest in China would want a smartphone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 314815.0,
      "end_time": 319800.0,
      "text": "and that they would do almost anything to get their hands on one."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 320893.0,
      "end_time": 323296.0,
      "text": "You have to keep in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 323321.0,
      "end_time": 326405.0,
      "text": "iPhones had just come out, it was 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 326429.0,
      "end_time": 328313.0,
      "text": "so this was, like, eight years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 328338.0,
      "end_time": 330775.0,
      "text": "and Androids had just started looking like iPhones."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 330799.0,
      "end_time": 333306.0,
      "text": "And a lot of very smart and realistic people said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 333330.0,
      "end_time": 335537.0,
      "text": "\"Those smartphones -- that&#39;s just a fad."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 336630.0,
      "end_time": 339580.0,
      "text": "Who wants to carry around these heavy things"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 339830.0,
      "end_time": 342570.0,
      "text": "where batteries drain quickly and they break every time you drop them?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 344613.0,
      "end_time": 345814.0,
      "text": "But I had a lot of data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 345838.0,
      "end_time": 348980.0,
      "text": "and I was very confident about my insights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 348122.0,
      "end_time": 350951.0,
      "text": "so I was very excited to share them with Nokia."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 353152.0,
      "end_time": 355669.0,
      "text": "But Nokia was not convinced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 355693.0,
      "end_time": 358270.0,
      "text": "because it wasn&#39;t big data."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 358842.0,
      "end_time": 361246.0,
      "text": "They said, \"We have millions of data points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 361270.0,
      "end_time": 365517.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t see any indicators of anyone wanting to buy a smartphone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 365541.0,
      "end_time": 369929.0,
      "text": "and your data set of 100, as diverse as it is, is too weak"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 369953.0,
      "end_time": 371667.0,
      "text": "for us to even take seriously.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 372728.0,
      "end_time": 374333.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"Nokia, you&#39;re right."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 374357.0,
      "end_time": 375917.0,
      "text": "Of course you wouldn&#39;t see this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 375941.0,
      "end_time": 379311.0,
      "text": "because you&#39;re sending out surveys assuming that people don&#39;t know"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 379336.0,
      "end_time": 380495.0,
      "text": "what a smartphone is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 380519.0,
      "end_time": 382885.0,
      "text": "so of course you&#39;re not going to get any data back"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 382909.0,
      "end_time": 385481.0,
      "text": "about people wanting to buy a smartphone in two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 385505.0,
      "end_time": 387623.0,
      "text": "Your surveys, your methods have been designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 387647.0,
      "end_time": 389669.0,
      "text": "to optimize an existing business model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 389693.0,
      "end_time": 392301.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m looking at these emergent human dynamics"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 392325.0,
      "end_time": 393679.0,
      "text": "that haven&#39;t happened yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 393703.0,
      "end_time": 396140.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re looking outside of market dynamics"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 396165.0,
      "end_time": 397796.0,
      "text": "so that we can get ahead of it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 399193.0,
      "end_time": 401437.0,
      "text": "Well, you know what happened to Nokia?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 401461.0,
      "end_time": 403826.0,
      "text": "Their business fell off a cliff."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 404611.0,
      "end_time": 408337.0,
      "text": "This -- this is the cost of missing something."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 408983.0,
      "end_time": 410982.0,
      "text": "It was unfathomable."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 411823.0,
      "end_time": 413474.0,
      "text": "But Nokia&#39;s not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 414780.0,
      "end_time": 416659.0,
      "text": "I see organizations throwing out data all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 416683.0,
      "end_time": 419244.0,
      "text": "because it didn&#39;t come from a quant model"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 419268.0,
      "end_time": 421350.0,
      "text": "or it doesn&#39;t fit in one."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 422390.0,
      "end_time": 424870.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not big data&#39;s fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 424762.0,
      "end_time": 428669.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the way we use big data; it&#39;s our responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 429550.0,
      "end_time": 431461.0,
      "text": "Big data&#39;s reputation for success"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 431485.0,
      "end_time": 435244.0,
      "text": "comes from quantifying very specific environments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 435268.0,
      "end_time": 440181.0,
      "text": "like electricity power grids or delivery logistics or genetic code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 440205.0,
      "end_time": 444522.0,
      "text": "when we&#39;re quantifying in systems that are more or less contained."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 444547.0,
      "end_time": 447516.0,
      "text": "But not all systems are as neatly contained."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 447540.0,
      "end_time": 450798.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re quantifying and systems are more dynamic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 450822.0,
      "end_time": 454621.0,
      "text": "especially systems that involve human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 454645.0,
      "end_time": 457700.0,
      "text": "forces are complex and unpredictable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 457950.0,
      "end_time": 460581.0,
      "text": "and these are things that we don&#39;t know how to model so well."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 461240.0,
      "end_time": 463837.0,
      "text": "Once you predict something about human behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 463861.0,
      "end_time": 465716.0,
      "text": "new factors emerge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 465740.0,
      "end_time": 468105.0,
      "text": "because conditions are constantly changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 468129.0,
      "end_time": 469932.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why it&#39;s a never-ending cycle."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 469956.0,
      "end_time": 471420.0,
      "text": "You think you know something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 471444.0,
      "end_time": 473686.0,
      "text": "and then something unknown enters the picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 473710.0,
      "end_time": 477320.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s why just relying on big data alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 477560.0,
      "end_time": 479905.0,
      "text": "increases the chance that we&#39;ll miss something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 479929.0,
      "end_time": 483705.0,
      "text": "while giving us this illusion that we already know everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 484226.0,
      "end_time": 488820.0,
      "text": "And what makes it really hard to see this paradox"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 488106.0,
      "end_time": 490765.0,
      "text": "and even wrap our brains around it"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 490789.0,
      "end_time": 494479.0,
      "text": "is that we have this thing that I call the quantification bias,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 494504.0,
      "end_time": 498426.0,
      "text": "which is the unconscious belief of valuing the measurable"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 498450.0,
      "end_time": 500440.0,
      "text": "over the immeasurable."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 501420.0,
      "end_time": 504325.0,
      "text": "And we often experience this at our work."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 504350.0,
      "end_time": 507000.0,
      "text": "Maybe we work alongside colleagues who are like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 507240.0,
      "end_time": 509452.0,
      "text": "or even our whole entire company may be like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 509476.0,
      "end_time": 512220.0,
      "text": "where people become so fixated on that number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 512460.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514113.00000000006,
      "text": "that they can&#39;t see anything outside of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 514135.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518839.99999999994,
      "text": "even when you present them evidence right in front of their face."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 518943.0,
      "end_time": 522313.0,
      "text": "And this is a very appealing message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 522337.0,
      "end_time": 524680.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s nothing wrong with quantifying;"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 524705.0,
      "end_time": 526135.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s actually very satisfying."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 526159.0,
      "end_time": 530521.0,
      "text": "I get a great sense of comfort from looking at an Excel spreadsheet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 530545.0,
      "end_time": 531945.0,
      "text": "even very simple ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 531970.0,
      "end_time": 532984.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 533800.0,
      "end_time": 534160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just kind of like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 534184.0,
      "end_time": 537688.0,
      "text": "\"Yes! The formula worked. It&#39;s all OK. Everything is under control.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 538612.0,
      "end_time": 541200.0,
      "text": "But the problem is"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 541260.0,
      "end_time": 543686.0,
      "text": "that quantifying is addictive."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 543711.0,
      "end_time": 545930.0,
      "text": "And when we forget that"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 545117.0,
      "end_time": 548155.0,
      "text": "and when we don&#39;t have something to kind of keep that in check,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 548179.0,
      "end_time": 550297.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s very easy to just throw out data"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 550321.0,
      "end_time": 553390.0,
      "text": "because it can&#39;t be expressed as a numerical value."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 553630.0,
      "end_time": 555984.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very easy just to slip into silver-bullet thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 556800.0,
      "end_time": 558587.0,
      "text": "as if some simple solution existed."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 559420.0,
      "end_time": 563482.0,
      "text": "Because this is a great moment of danger for any organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 563506.0,
      "end_time": 566140.0,
      "text": "because oftentimes, the future we need to predict --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 566164.0,
      "end_time": 568330.0,
      "text": "it isn&#39;t in that haystack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 568354.0,
      "end_time": 570892.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s that tornado that&#39;s bearing down on us"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 570916.0,
      "end_time": 572404.0,
      "text": "outside of the barn."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 574780.0,
      "end_time": 577106.0,
      "text": "There is no greater risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 577130.0,
      "end_time": 578796.0,
      "text": "than being blind to the unknown."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 578820.0,
      "end_time": 580969.0,
      "text": "It can cause you to make the wrong decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 580993.0,
      "end_time": 582967.0,
      "text": "It can cause you to miss something big."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 583554.0,
      "end_time": 586655.0,
      "text": "But we don&#39;t have to go down this path."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587273.0,
      "end_time": 590468.0,
      "text": "It turns out that the oracle of ancient Greece"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 590492.0,
      "end_time": 594458.0,
      "text": "holds the secret key that shows us the path forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 595474.0,
      "end_time": 598690.0,
      "text": "Now, recent geological research has shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 598930.0,
      "end_time": 601656.0,
      "text": "that the Temple of Apollo, where the most famous oracle sat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 601681.0,
      "end_time": 604765.0,
      "text": "was actually built over two earthquake faults."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 604789.0,
      "end_time": 607675.0,
      "text": "And these faults would release these petrochemical fumes"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 607699.0,
      "end_time": 609383.0,
      "text": "from underneath the Earth&#39;s crust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 609408.0,
      "end_time": 613274.0,
      "text": "and the oracle literally sat right above these faults,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 613298.0,
      "end_time": 616886.0,
      "text": "inhaling enormous amounts of ethylene gas, these fissures."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 616910.0,
      "end_time": 617918.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 617942.0,
      "end_time": 619115.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 619139.0,
      "end_time": 620156.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 620180.0,
      "end_time": 623689.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all true, and that&#39;s what made her babble and hallucinate"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 623713.0,
      "end_time": 625437.0,
      "text": "and go into this trance-like state."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 625461.0,
      "end_time": 627231.0,
      "text": "She was high as a kite!"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 627255.0,
      "end_time": 631716.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 631740.0,
      "end_time": 634519.0,
      "text": "So how did anyone --"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 634543.0,
      "end_time": 637573.0,
      "text": "How did anyone get any useful advice out of her"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 637597.0,
      "end_time": 638787.0,
      "text": "in this state?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 639317.0,
      "end_time": 641698.0,
      "text": "Well, you see those people surrounding the oracle?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 641722.0,
      "end_time": 643601.0,
      "text": "You see those people holding her up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 643625.0,
      "end_time": 645342.0,
      "text": "because she&#39;s, like, a little woozy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 645366.0,
      "end_time": 647674.0,
      "text": "And you see that guy on your left-hand side"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 647698.0,
      "end_time": 649295.0,
      "text": "holding the orange notebook?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 649925.0,
      "end_time": 651655.0,
      "text": "Well, those were the temple guides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 651679.0,
      "end_time": 654694.0,
      "text": "and they worked hand in hand with the oracle."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 655904.0,
      "end_time": 658420.0,
      "text": "When inquisitors would come and get on their knees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 658444.0,
      "end_time": 660784.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s when the temple guides would get to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 660808.0,
      "end_time": 662672.0,
      "text": "because after they asked her questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 662696.0,
      "end_time": 664697.0,
      "text": "they would observe their emotional state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 664721.0,
      "end_time": 667450.0,
      "text": "and then they would ask them follow-up questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 667690.0,
      "end_time": 669902.0,
      "text": "like, \"Why do you want to know this prophecy? Who are you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 669927.0,
      "end_time": 672191.0,
      "text": "What are you going to do with this information?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 672215.0,
      "end_time": 675397.0,
      "text": "And then the temple guides would take this more ethnographic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 675421.0,
      "end_time": 677577.0,
      "text": "this more qualitative information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 677601.0,
      "end_time": 679676.0,
      "text": "and interpret the oracle&#39;s babblings."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 681248.0,
      "end_time": 683540.0,
      "text": "So the oracle didn&#39;t stand alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 683564.0,
      "end_time": 685712.0,
      "text": "and neither should our big data systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 686450.0,
      "end_time": 687611.0,
      "text": "Now to be clear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 687635.0,
      "end_time": 691930.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not saying that big data systems are huffing ethylene gas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 691118.0,
      "end_time": 693471.0,
      "text": "or that they&#39;re even giving invalid predictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 693495.0,
      "end_time": 694656.0,
      "text": "The total opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 694680.0,
      "end_time": 696747.0,
      "text": "But what I am saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 696772.0,
      "end_time": 700604.0,
      "text": "is that in the same way that the oracle needed her temple guides,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 700628.0,
      "end_time": 702916.0,
      "text": "our big data systems need them, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 702940.0,
      "end_time": 707490.0,
      "text": "They need people like ethnographers and user researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 707730.0,
      "end_time": 709579.0,
      "text": "who can gather what I call thick data."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 710322.0,
      "end_time": 713313.0,
      "text": "This is precious data from humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 713337.0,
      "end_time": 717439.0,
      "text": "like stories, emotions and interactions that cannot be quantified."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 717463.0,
      "end_time": 719785.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the kind of data that I collected for Nokia"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 719809.0,
      "end_time": 722478.0,
      "text": "that comes in in the form of a very small sample size,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 722502.0,
      "end_time": 725457.0,
      "text": "but delivers incredible depth of meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 725481.0,
      "end_time": 729161.0,
      "text": "And what makes it so thick and meaty"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 730265.0,
      "end_time": 734294.0,
      "text": "is the experience of understanding the human narrative."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 734318.0,
      "end_time": 737957.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what helps to see what&#39;s missing in our models."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 738671.0,
      "end_time": 742716.0,
      "text": "Thick data grounds our business questions in human questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 742740.0,
      "end_time": 746302.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why integrating big and thick data"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 746326.0,
      "end_time": 748150.0,
      "text": "forms a more complete picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 748592.0,
      "end_time": 751473.0,
      "text": "Big data is able to offer insights at scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 751497.0,
      "end_time": 754144.0,
      "text": "and leverage the best of machine intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 754168.0,
      "end_time": 757740.0,
      "text": "whereas thick data can help us rescue the context loss"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 757764.0,
      "end_time": 759862.0,
      "text": "that comes from making big data usable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 759886.0,
      "end_time": 762670.0,
      "text": "and leverage the best of human intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 762910.0,
      "end_time": 765643.0,
      "text": "And when you actually integrate the two, that&#39;s when things get really fun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 765667.0,
      "end_time": 768103.0,
      "text": "because then you&#39;re no longer just working with data"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 768127.0,
      "end_time": 769323.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve already collected."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 769347.0,
      "end_time": 772840.0,
      "text": "You get to also work with data that hasn&#39;t been collected."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 772108.0,
      "end_time": 773827.0,
      "text": "You get to ask questions about why:"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 773851.0,
      "end_time": 775168.0,
      "text": "Why is this happening?"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 775598.0,
      "end_time": 776977.0,
      "text": "Now, when Netflix did this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 777100.0,
      "end_time": 780360.0,
      "text": "they unlocked a whole new way to transform their business."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 781226.0,
      "end_time": 785182.0,
      "text": "Netflix is known for their really great recommendation algorithm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 785206.0,
      "end_time": 790300.0,
      "text": "and they had this $1 million prize for anyone who could improve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 790270.0,
      "end_time": 791341.0,
      "text": "And there were winners."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 792750.0,
      "end_time": 796398.0,
      "text": "But Netflix discovered the improvements were only incremental."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 797224.0,
      "end_time": 799188.0,
      "text": "So to really find out what was going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 799212.0,
      "end_time": 802953.0,
      "text": "they hired an ethnographer, Grant McCracken,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 802977.0,
      "end_time": 804523.0,
      "text": "to gather thick data insights."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 804547.0,
      "end_time": 808471.0,
      "text": "And what he discovered was something that they hadn&#39;t seen initially"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 808495.0,
      "end_time": 809850.0,
      "text": "in the quantitative data."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 810892.0,
      "end_time": 813620.0,
      "text": "He discovered that people loved to binge-watch."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 813644.0,
      "end_time": 815997.0,
      "text": "In fact, people didn&#39;t even feel guilty about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 816210.0,
      "end_time": 817276.0,
      "text": "They enjoyed it."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 817300.0,
      "end_time": 818325.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 818350.0,
      "end_time": 820706.0,
      "text": "So Netflix was like, \"Oh. This is a new insight.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 820730.0,
      "end_time": 822668.0,
      "text": "So they went to their data science team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 822692.0,
      "end_time": 825100.0,
      "text": "and they were able to scale this big data insight"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 825340.0,
      "end_time": 827621.0,
      "text": "in with their quantitative data."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 827645.0,
      "end_time": 830814.0,
      "text": "And once they verified it and validated it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 830839.0,
      "end_time": 835600.0,
      "text": "Netflix decided to do something very simple but impactful."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 836654.0,
      "end_time": 843146.0,
      "text": "They said, instead of offering the same show from different genres"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 843170.0,
      "end_time": 847580.0,
      "text": "or more of the different shows from similar users,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 847820.0,
      "end_time": 849636.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll just offer more of the same show."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 849660.0,
      "end_time": 851765.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll make it easier for you to binge-watch."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 851789.0,
      "end_time": 853275.0,
      "text": "And they didn&#39;t stop there."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 853299.0,
      "end_time": 854773.0,
      "text": "They did all these things"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 854797.0,
      "end_time": 857756.0,
      "text": "to redesign their entire viewer experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 857780.0,
      "end_time": 859538.0,
      "text": "to really encourage binge-watching."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 860500.0,
      "end_time": 863290.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s why people and friends disappear for whole weekends at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 863315.0,
      "end_time": 865658.0,
      "text": "catching up on shows like \"Master of None.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 865682.0,
      "end_time": 869855.0,
      "text": "By integrating big data and thick data, they not only improved their business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 869879.0,
      "end_time": 872691.0,
      "text": "but they transformed how we consume media."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 872715.0,
      "end_time": 877267.0,
      "text": "And now their stocks are projected to double in the next few years."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 878100.0,
      "end_time": 881930.0,
      "text": "But this isn&#39;t just about watching more videos"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 881954.0,
      "end_time": 883574.0,
      "text": "or selling more smartphones."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 883963.0,
      "end_time": 888120.0,
      "text": "For some, integrating thick data insights into the algorithm"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 888370.0,
      "end_time": 890300.0,
      "text": "could mean life or death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 890324.0,
      "end_time": 892469.0,
      "text": "especially for the marginalized."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 893558.0,
      "end_time": 896992.0,
      "text": "All around the country, police departments are using big data"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 897160.0,
      "end_time": 898978.0,
      "text": "for predictive policing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 899300.0,
      "end_time": 902870.0,
      "text": "to set bond amounts and sentencing recommendations"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 902111.0,
      "end_time": 905258.0,
      "text": "in ways that reinforce existing biases."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 906116.0,
      "end_time": 908539.0,
      "text": "NSA&#39;s Skynet machine learning algorithm"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 908563.0,
      "end_time": 914700.0,
      "text": "has possibly aided in the deaths of thousands of civilians in Pakistan"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 914310.0,
      "end_time": 916752.0,
      "text": "from misreading cellular device metadata."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 918951.0,
      "end_time": 922354.0,
      "text": "As all of our lives become more automated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 922378.0,
      "end_time": 925458.0,
      "text": "from automobiles to health insurance or to employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 925482.0,
      "end_time": 927832.0,
      "text": "it is likely that all of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 927856.0,
      "end_time": 930845.0,
      "text": "will be impacted by the quantification bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 932792.0,
      "end_time": 935413.0,
      "text": "Now, the good news is that we&#39;ve come a long way"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 935437.0,
      "end_time": 937887.0,
      "text": "from huffing ethylene gas to make predictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 937911.0,
      "end_time": 940981.0,
      "text": "We have better tools, so let&#39;s just use them better."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 941500.0,
      "end_time": 943328.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s integrate the big data with the thick data."
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 943352.0,
      "end_time": 945613.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s bring our temple guides with the oracles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 945637.0,
      "end_time": 949120.0,
      "text": "and whether this work happens in companies or nonprofits"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 949370.0,
      "end_time": 951506.0,
      "text": "or government or even in the software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 951530.0,
      "end_time": 953322.0,
      "text": "all of it matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 953346.0,
      "end_time": 956369.0,
      "text": "because that means we&#39;re collectively committed"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 956393.0,
      "end_time": 958584.0,
      "text": "to making better data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 958608.0,
      "end_time": 960444.0,
      "text": "better algorithms, better outputs"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 960468.0,
      "end_time": 962111.0,
      "text": "and better decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 962135.0,
      "end_time": 965693.0,
      "text": "This is how we&#39;ll avoid missing that something."
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 967420.0,
      "end_time": 970990.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}